en_127554_0	Al-Qaeda leader Osama Bin Laden has left a fortune of $21 million inheritance for jihad, his will shows.
en_127554_1	Foreign media reported that the will was seized during the US raid in Abbottabad in Pakistan.
en_127554_2	In the will Bin Laden has asked his family to ‘obey my will’ and spend the money on ‘jihad, for the sake of Allah’.
en_127554_3	Bin Laden was killed by US Special Forces in May 2011 during the Abbottabad raid.
